
~~~ 
<h3 id="1">1: Test: Add comment in Project.toml</h3>
~~~
tags: *test, julia*

A test pattern to see if things work.
~~~
<pre><code class="plaintext">match='name = ":[name]"' 

rewrite='''
# A new comment.
name = ":[name]"'''
</code></pre>
~~~


~~~ 
<h3 id="2">2: Avoid var === nothing</h3>
~~~
tags: *julia*

Note that `ismissing` can be slower, see <https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/issues/27681>.
~~~
<pre><code class="plaintext">match='if :[var] === nothing' 

rewrite='if isnothing(:[var])'
</code></pre>
~~~


~~~ 
<h3 id="3">3: Avoid var !== nothing</h3>
~~~
tags: *julia*

See [pattern 2](#2).
~~~
<pre><code class="plaintext">match='if :[var] !== nothing'

rewrite='if !isnothing(:[var])'
</code></pre>
~~~


~~~ 
<h3 id="4">4: Replace Array{T,1} with Vector{T}</h3>
~~~
tags: *julia*

Vector{T} is an alias for Array{T,1}.
~~~
<pre><code class="plaintext">match='Array{:[T],1}'

rewrite='Vector{:[T]}'
</code></pre>
~~~

